title: Seizures induced by combined levomepromazine-fluvoxamine treatment.
abst: We report a case of combined levomepromazine-fluvoxamine treatment-induced seizures. It seems that combined treatment of fluvoxamine with phenothiazines may possess proconvulsive activity.
